sql_query:
SELECT *
FROM prices AS p
    INNER JOIN hospitals AS h ON p.npi_number = h.npi_number
    INNER JOIN cpt_hcpcs AS c ON p.code = c.code
WHERE h.npi_number = "1003389206"
    OR h.npi_number = "1003873225"
    OR h.npi_number = "1003887266"
    OR h.npi_number = "1003905092"
    OR h.npi_number = "1013176544"
    OR h.npi_number = "1023003969"
    OR h.npi_number = "1023057809"
    OR h.npi_number = "1023061405"
    OR h.npi_number = "1023180502"
    OR h.npi_number = "1043323918"
